overview: Leilani crashes her daddy’s car. When she brings the car to the body shop she finds out she doesn’t have enough money for the repairs. So in exchange for the body work, she agrees to have her body worked by everyone in the garage.  Jayden throws a surprise party for her dad. But the party almost ends abruptly when he’s late and hs friends threaten to leave. The party turns into a real surprise when she agrees to entertain all of his friends.
title: Teen Gang Bangs
